03:17.320 --> 03:19.000
 of anyone who tries to hold on

03:19.000 --> 03:23.280
 and leave behind an empty shell of a human being.

03:24.360 --> 03:27.120
 I prefer to die a man who lived by principles

03:27.120 --> 03:28.760
 that nobody could shake

03:28.760 --> 03:31.640
 and a man who added a bit of love to the world.

