 Cause you don't know what would have happened if the person had not been vaccinated.

1:16:06.160 --> 1:16:09.160
 So you have to have some control group.

1:16:09.160 --> 1:16:14.160
 Now what happened is there's several systems to do, to check this in that the CDC uses.

